<p>by motor ambulance, &amp; in some cases the family as well.<br/>How can I write what I felt when I saw the pitiful sight of those poor people in the dangers of shell fire, &amp; the desolateness of leaving their homes.<br/>X x<br/>News has just arrived that B Section (my own) is to be prepared to move at a moment's notice. I have been expecting that <strike>for</strike> to happen since I arrived</p>
